data.value: Step 1: Select which VRX to use Step 2: Enter the VRX IP Step 3: Click [Generate keys] Step 4: Click [Receive drone.key] Step 5: Reboot the VRX Step 6: Select the option [OpenIPC Camera] Step 7: Enter the OpenIPC camera IP Step 8: Click [Send drone.key] Step 9: Reboot OpenIPC camera
